reviewText: Steve was very informative and made me feel like Icould do one too.  Loved the video.
Steve's dvd's are great! He gets to the point while taking you step by step. I have purchased 3 of his instructional dvds. Thanks Steve Backus!
My husband loved it. It arrived on time and in good shape. Thank you.

This video is a great way for a beginner to learn how to chainsaw carve an eagle.  Steve adds his own bit of humor to the video but it is step by step and in detail.  If you are a beginner, this is a must have!
